description: Zhaoheng Hydropower Ltd. engages in the generation and supply of hydropower in southwestern and midwestern China. The company involves in the investment, operation, and development of small- to medium-sized hydropower plants. It serves primarily power grid companies that engage in electricity transmission and distribution. As of December 31, 2008, Zhaoheng Hydropower owned and operated 17 generating units with an installed capacity of approximately 132.85 megawatts. The company is headquartered in Shenzhen, People's Republic of China.
